&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot; data-sourcepos=&quot;19:1-19:128;1727-1854&quot;&gt;Partner closely with Technical Account Managers to monitor delivery, proactively analyze performance, and optimize campaigns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot; data-sourcepos=&quot;20:1-20:112;1855-1966&quot;&gt;Find and close expansion opportunities within your book of business — thoughtful upsell, not checkbox upsell.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot; data-sourcepos=&quot;21:1-21:177;1967-2143&quot

&lt;p&gt;Eulerity is a leading marketing technology company simplifying digital advertising for franchises and multi-location businesses. We use machine learning and automation to help our clients scale. We are currently in a pivotal &quot;0 to 1&quot; phase regarding our financial infrastructure and need a hands-on leader to professionalize our accounting and prepare us for future growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a leader in Finance who is fundamentally a builder and uses AI tools. Your immediate priority will be to take full ownership of our financial operations, ensuring our books are impeccable and our cash flow is managed with precision.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;While this role requires a strategic mind capable of handling future fundraising (venture debt/equity) as the company evolves, &lt;strong&gt;your primary focus today will be operational.&lt;/strong&gt; You will be the sole owner of the finance function, managing pass-through costs, reconciliations, and financial reporting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Immediate Priorities: Accounting &amp;amp; Operations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own the General Ledger:&lt;/strong&gt; Manage day-to-day accounting operations including AP/AR, payroll, and the general ledger. Ensure all data is accurate and up to date.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Media Spend Management:&lt;/strong&gt; Actively manage and reconcile &lt;strong&gt;pass-through media costs&lt;/strong&gt;. You must understand the difference between gross vs. net revenue in an AdTech context and ensure client media budgets are accounted for correctly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cash Flow Control:&lt;/strong&gt; rigorous monitoring of cash flow, burn rate, and runway. You will provide leadership with accurate, real-time views of the company’s liquidity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Month-End Close:&lt;/strong&gt; Establish and execute a disciplined month-end close process, producing timely financial statements (P&amp;amp;L, Balance Sheet, Cash Flow).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Systems Implementation:&lt;/strong&gt; Move us from early-stage startup processes to professional financial workflows. Implement controls and software stacks (e.g., billing, expense management) that scale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Future Focus: Strategy &amp;amp; Growth&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Financial Readiness:&lt;/strong&gt; Ensure our financial historicals and models are structured in a way that will support due diligence when the time comes for fundraising.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Modeling:&lt;/strong&gt; Build financial models to forecast growth scenarios and assist the CEO in long-term planning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Capital Markets:&lt;/strong&gt; As we approach future financing rounds, partner with the CEO/CTO/COO to navigate debt and equity financing, utilizing your knowledge of Venture Capital and Venture Debt structures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience:&lt;/strong&gt; 5+ years of hands-on finance/accounting experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Industry Fit:&lt;/strong&gt; Experience in &lt;strong&gt;AdTech, MarTech, or Digital Agencies&lt;/strong&gt; is preferred. You must be comfortable handling high-volume media pass-throughs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The &quot;0 to 1&quot; Builder:&lt;/strong&gt; You have experience setting up financial systems in a startup environment. You are not looking for a team to delegate to; you are looking to do the work yourself.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Proficiency:&lt;/strong&gt; Expert in QuickBooks Online (or Xero) and Excel.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fundraising Literacy

&lt;p&gt;Eulerity is an AI-native marketing automation platform — not a legacy tool with AI bolted on. We serve enterprise brands including Mastercard, UPS Store, Uber Eats, and European Wax Center, automating digital advertising across thousands of franchise and multi-location businesses.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are hiring Customer Success Managers to own the client relationships that sit at the center of what we do. This role is open at multiple levels — we are looking for sharp, curious people earlier in their account management careers as well as senior operators who have run large books of business. Level and compensation will be calibrated to experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who we are looking for&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Someone who knows the difference between a client who is satisfied and a client who is actually growing and who cares about the difference. You are as comfortable in a campaign dashboard as you are in a client conversation. You do not wait for clients to surface problems; you spot the pattern before it becomes one. And when you make a recommendation, you can show your work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will actually do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary point of contact for a portfolio of multi-location and franchise brands the person they call when something matters.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run onboarding sessions that set the tone for a long-term partnership from day one.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and lead campaign and business reviews that go beyond reporting — surface the real story in the data and come with a clear point of view on what to do next.&lt;/li&gt;
